snippet.textDisplay: I was so sad to hear about Frys! I spent a lot of time and money there in my late teens and twenties. Loved all the different themes. The one in my hometown was kind of computer history themed. Mayan one was pretty cool, Egyptian and Western themed ones were kinda ridiculous, Californians World Fair theme one was bad ass with the huge Jacobs ladder inside, and the Railroad history themed one in the Sacramento area was pretty cool as well. But I won’t miss their horrible inventory tracking and control. How do you manage to lose almost 30 high end CPU’s between 3 stores that all claim to have multiple of them in store, yet can’t find a single one! 🤣😂😂
